Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:04.94,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}翻譯：傻瓜三世 ZERO 逆火 校對：傻瓜三世\N\N後期：Misaki喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰叫你穿那麼厚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以不用練了吧 比賽都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可不行 回程還有一場跳長繩大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到獲勝隊伍是吃什麼肉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼可以吊車尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少不能再吃魚肉香腸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為那可不算肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨好會跳繩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是奇怪 就是你給人不會跳的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨是人不可貌相的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比方說不可貌相的蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可貌相的急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可貌相的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜歡你！
