Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn華康中特圓體\bord3\b0\1c&H80B8DD&\3c&H4A5150&\fs50\frz5.136\pos(634,238)\frx346\fry356}霜淇淋日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.86,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@華康少女文字W5\bord0\fs30\1c&HA0CFCE&\pos(898,390)\frz285.5}來吃霜淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是什麼樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 隊長的性格啊男性關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛都說了 她只是我媽的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒怎麼跟她聊過天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去買點高麗菜 幫我顧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 找零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 您的找零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能把錢給不認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很正經？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我感覺跟正經有點差別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的戀愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪知道 那時候我還在上幼稚園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能當面問她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是請她接受採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聊著聊著轉個彎把問題拋出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像藝人開記者會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交往順利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要問我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 誰去採訪問問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前好像也發生過類似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼不願意 出發前晚在甲板上聊過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為我們沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你們關係挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道你們關係不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是不好吧 怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有距離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你們在甲板上聊過天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你們關係挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那只是偶然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們本來就都不擅長說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以貴子一離開 我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒有孩子 不知道該跟她聊什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再說了 貴子實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的不想跟她聊聊貴子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子總是說 媽媽在等她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搜索中止了 是我做的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓你們久等了 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉提了個不情之請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 報瀨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她還有點別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}攝影機就位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 你們打算問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天想採訪一下隊長的私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡的食物 日常生活等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有戀愛之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是你喜歡什麼樣的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會回答和南極觀測無關的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟 人家高中生在問你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近播放數下滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耳朵好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊長 您剛洗完澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡什麼入浴劑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老實說 喜歡什麼類型？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}眼睛再大一點會不會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保持原樣就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據說已經進入南極圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太陽不會沉下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像雲一樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 但她就是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算說是雲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高雲 中雲 低雲也各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無聊透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好大的雲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雲可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明抓不到 但抬個頭就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪懂那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還是能意會一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}採訪結果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她沒關係 是我想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道隊長和小淵澤的女兒關係還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是出於好奇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是還沒有原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可是個大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是隊長 有義務跟隊員溝通確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:24.81,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天〇八〇〇至一二〇〇允許艦上運動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.35,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺超痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬天運動經常會這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你懂了嗎 像雲一樣是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多少少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快告訴我啊 到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難以 言傳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子 你是故意讓我和那孩子獨處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對啊 因為那孩子需要小吟的靈魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}噓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想聽聽你是怎麼看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想聽我說恨你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從媽媽登上民間觀測船開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就問了她很多遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她說南極觀測還有很多危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你還是要去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道南極是個什麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我那時是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你犯了什麼錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是判斷失誤 才把我媽媽留在南極的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當時別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 最後讓我問一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是真心的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真心這麼想的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才討厭談這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本不知道自己是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是…只是媽媽沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我每天的生活並沒有變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和等她回來的每一天完全一樣 什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我日日夜夜都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彷彿自己還在等媽媽回來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要改變這種生活 我就得出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去那片 比宇宙還要遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷慢速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷慢速後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撞上固定冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是要開到冰上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 要先大幅度後退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷停止 兩舷慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兩舷停止 兩舷慢速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝進冰層裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用船體的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破壞冰層
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才叫破冰船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果冰層沒碎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就一直重複
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重複到冰層破碎為止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到南極真的好艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤其這一帶是出了名的難靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼偏偏要挑這個地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為只有這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極觀測正規化 是在第二次世界大戰後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道這些嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戰敗國的日本想派遣觀測隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多國家都對此不信任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再加上日本沒什麼發言權
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後被分到的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是被公認為不可能靠岸的東翁古爾島這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是被刁難了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道有沒有被刁難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過可能拐彎抹角地包含了這層意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就好像在說「日本人 你們有本事就來啊」似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽起來真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過大家聽了都熱血起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全日本募款資助計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}造船工人們嘔心瀝血造出了觀測船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次一次又一次 絕不言棄奮力拚搏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像破開冰層一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二強速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}衝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒 還早著呢 得一直到我們抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年又一年 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子 貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 小淵澤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.98,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是…美極了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:06.02,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっと記した夢　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:16.74,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:25.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:30.79,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:38.93,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:45.35,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:49.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:54.40,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:59.36,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:09.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:14.92,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南風はやがて島を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:19.26,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:30.60,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}小さな夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:35.36,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}願えた　ツヨクツヨク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.94,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}履き慣れたスニーカー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:44.62,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紐をギュッと締め直して
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:50.04,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}でかい夢を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:54.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハルカ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.21,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:04.14,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}進んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:08.64,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:06.02,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷記下了夢想 卻只找了一堆藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:16.74,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己總是忘記夢想 就怕去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:25.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什麼事 怕有什麼變故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:30.79,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但駐足不前 就什麼都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:38.93,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 邁出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:45.35,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:49.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:54.40,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:59.36,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:09.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}紅紅的一輪夕陽 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:14.92,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南風跨越萬千島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:19.26,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹動起我的髮梢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:30.60,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底小小的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:35.36,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用力再用力 向神明許願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:37.94,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}穿上熟悉的運動鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:44.62,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}緊緊地繫好鞋帶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:50.04,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想實現心底大大的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:54.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遙遠不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:59.21,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波濤之中舉杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:04.14,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}繼續一步步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:08.64,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是真的真的真的 想為隊長做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是她完全沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隊員哪幫得了隊長 人家也不會讓你幫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把你的心情 交給一個你碰得到人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 沒有這回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我之前是怎麼塞進箱子裡的 好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收拾好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你能睜眼說瞎話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小結 帶上攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能下去感受一下 半徑5公尺以內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終點！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}報瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是你媽媽來過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨慕吧 嫉妒吧 恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你們趾高氣昂地嘲笑我 我也相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你們以不可能為由背叛我 我也沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 我到南極了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羨慕吧！嫉妒吧！恨吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就想說這些？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}壓抑了很久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼關係 這才是報瀨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2 活該
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1 2 活該
Comment: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:24.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}長いトンネルの出口を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:35.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}かすかな光の匂いがしてる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:41.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}間違っても　笑えるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:52.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}ここから始めよう　僕は旅に出よう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:23:03.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}汚れた真ん丸のビー玉　握りしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:14.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}言えなかった言葉も　きっと見つかるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:19.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}バカにされたって構わない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:25.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}信じてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:24.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}尋找著漫長隧道的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:35.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}向著泛著微光氣味的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:41.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}就算走錯了 也別忘了微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:52.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}從這裡開始 我將踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:23:03.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}緊緊捏住手心裡 髒髒的玻璃珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:14.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}沒說出口的話 我也一定會找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:19.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}隨你們嘲笑吧 我不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:25.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}要相信自己 邁出腳步
